<?xml version="1.0" encoding="ISO-8859-1"?>
<wfs:WFS_Capabilities xmlns:gml="http://www.opengis.net/gml" xmlns:wfs="http://www.opengis.net/wfs" xmlns:ows="http://www.opengis.net/ows" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xmlns:ogc="http://www.opengis.net/ogc" xmlns="http://www.opengis.net/wfs" version="1.1.0" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.opengis.net/wfs http://schemas.opengis.net/wfs/1.1.0/wfs.xsd">
  <ows:ServiceIdentification>
    <ows:Title>NURE_Sediment_Geochemistry</ows:Title>
    <ows:Abstract>National-scale geochemical analysis of stream sediments and soils in the US collected and analyzed under the National Uranium Resource Evaluation program.</ows:Abstract>
    <ows:Keywords>
      <ows:Keyword>geochemistry; unconsolidated deposits; chemical analysis</ows:Keyword>
    </ows:Keywords>
    <ows:ServiceType codeSpace="OGC">OGC WFS</ows:ServiceType>
    <ows:ServiceTypeVersion>1.1.0</ows:ServiceTypeVersion>
    <ows:Fees>none</ows:Fees>
    <ows:AccessConstraints>none</ows:AccessConstraints>
  </ows:ServiceIdentification>
  <ows:ServiceProvider>
    <ows:ProviderName>U.S. Geological Survey Mineral Resources Program</ows:ProviderName>
    <ows:ProviderSite xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="http://mrdata.usgs.gov/"/>
    <ows:ServiceContact>
      <ows:IndividualName>Peter N. Schweitzer</ows:IndividualName>
      <ows:PositionName>Geologist</ows:PositionName>
      <ows:ContactInfo>
        <ows:Phone>
          <ows:Voice>703-648-6533</ows:Voice>
          <ows:Facsimile>703-648-6252</ows:Facsimile>
        </ows:Phone>
        <ows:Address>
          <ows:DeliveryPoint>Mail Stop 954 USGS National Center</ows:DeliveryPoint>
          <ows:City>Reston</ows:City>
          <ows:AdministrativeArea>VA</ows:AdministrativeArea>
          <ows:PostalCode>20192</ows:PostalCode>
          <ows:Country>USA</ows:Country>
          <ows:ElectronicMailAddress>pschweitzer@usgs.gov</ows:ElectronicMailAddress>
        </ows:Address>
        <ows:OnlineResource xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="http://mrdata.usgs.gov/"/>
        <ows:HoursOfService>M-F 9:00am-5:30pm EST/EDT</ows:HoursOfService>
        <ows:ContactInstructions>Alternate email address: ask@usgs.gov</ows:ContactInstructions>
      </ows:ContactInfo>
      <ows:Role>distributor</ows:Role>
    </ows:ServiceContact>
  </ows:ServiceProvider>
  <ows:OperationsMetadata>
    <ows:Operation name="GetCapabilities">
      <ows:DCP>
        <ows:HTTP>
          <ows:Get xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="http://mrdata.usgs.gov/wfs/nuresed?"/>
          <ows:Post xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="http://mrdata.usgs.gov/wfs/nuresed?"/>
        </ows:HTTP>
      </ows:DCP>
      <ows:Parameter name="service">
        <ows:Value>WFS</ows:Value>
      </ows:Parameter>
      <ows:Parameter name="AcceptVersions">
        <ows:Value>1.0.0</ows:Value>
        <ows:Value>1.1.0</ows:Value>
      </ows:Parameter>
      <ows:Parameter name="AcceptFormats">
        <ows:Value>text/xml</ows:Value>
      </ows:Parameter>
    </ows:Operation>
    <ows:Operation name="DescribeFeatureType">
      <ows:DCP>
        <ows:HTTP>
          <ows:Get xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="http://mrdata.usgs.gov/wfs/nuresed?"/>
          <ows:Post xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="http://mrdata.usgs.gov/wfs/nuresed?"/>
        </ows:HTTP>
      </ows:DCP>
      <ows:Parameter name="outputFormat">
        <ows:Value>XMLSCHEMA</ows:Value>
        <ows:Value>text/xml; subtype=gml/2.1.2</ows:Value>
        <ows:Value>text/xml; subtype=gml/3.1.1</ows:Value>
      </ows:Parameter>
    </ows:Operation>
    <ows:Operation name="GetFeature">
      <ows:DCP>
        <ows:HTTP>
          <ows:Get xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="http://mrdata.usgs.gov/wfs/nuresed?"/>
          <ows:Post xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="http://mrdata.usgs.gov/wfs/nuresed?"/>
        </ows:HTTP>
      </ows:DCP>
      <ows:Parameter name="resultType">
        <ows:Value>results</ows:Value>
        <ows:Value>hits</ows:Value>
      </ows:Parameter>
      <ows:Parameter name="outputFormat">
        <ows:Value>text/xml; subtype=gml/3.1.1</ows:Value>
      </ows:Parameter>
    </ows:Operation>
  </ows:OperationsMetadata>
  <FeatureTypeList>
    <Operations>
      <Operation>Query</Operation>
    </Operations>
    <FeatureType>
      <Name>nuresed</Name>
      <Title>nuresed</Title>
      <Abstract>National-scale geochemical analysis of stream sediments and soils in the US collected and analyzed under the National Uranium Resource Evaluation program.</Abstract>
      <ows:Keywords>
        <ows:Keyword>geochemistry; unconsolidated deposits; chemical analysis</ows:Keyword>
      </ows:Keywords>
      <DefaultSRS>urn:ogc:def:crs:EPSG::4326</DefaultSRS>
      <OutputFormats>
        <Format>text/xml; subtype=gml/3.1.1</Format>
      </OutputFormats>
      <ows:WGS84BoundingBox dimensions="2">
        <ows:LowerCorner>-169 25</ows:LowerCorner>
        <ows:UpperCorner>-66 72</ows:UpperCorner>
      </ows:WGS84BoundingBox>
      <MetadataURL format="text/xml" type="FGDC">http://mrdata.usgs.gov/metadata/nurehssr.xml</MetadataURL>
    </FeatureType>
  </FeatureTypeList>
  <ogc:Filter_Capabilities>
    <ogc:Spatial_Capabilities>
      <ogc:GeometryOperands>
        <ogc:GeometryOperand>gml:Point</ogc:GeometryOperand>
        <ogc:GeometryOperand>gml:LineString</ogc:GeometryOperand>
        <ogc:GeometryOperand>gml:Polygon</ogc:GeometryOperand>
        <ogc:GeometryOperand>gml:Envelope</ogc:GeometryOperand>
      </ogc:GeometryOperands>
      <ogc:SpatialOperators>
        <ogc:SpatialOperator name="Equals"/>
        <ogc:SpatialOperator name="Disjoint"/>
        <ogc:SpatialOperator name="Touches"/>
        <ogc:SpatialOperator name="Within"/>
        <ogc:SpatialOperator name="Overlaps"/>
        <ogc:SpatialOperator name="Crosses"/>
        <ogc:SpatialOperator name="Intersects"/>
        <ogc:SpatialOperator name="Contains"/>
        <ogc:SpatialOperator name="DWithin"/>
        <ogc:SpatialOperator name="Beyond"/>
        <ogc:SpatialOperator name="BBOX"/>
      </ogc:SpatialOperators>
    </ogc:Spatial_Capabilities>
    <ogc:Scalar_Capabilities>
      <ogc:LogicalOperators/>
      <ogc:ComparisonOperators>
        <ogc:ComparisonOperator>LessThan</ogc:ComparisonOperator>
        <ogc:ComparisonOperator>GreaterThan</ogc:ComparisonOperator>
        <ogc:ComparisonOperator>LessThanEqualTo</ogc:ComparisonOperator>
        <ogc:ComparisonOperator>GreaterThanEqualTo</ogc:ComparisonOperator>
        <ogc:ComparisonOperator>EqualTo</ogc:ComparisonOperator>
        <ogc:ComparisonOperator>NotEqualTo</ogc:ComparisonOperator>
        <ogc:ComparisonOperator>Like</ogc:ComparisonOperator>
        <ogc:ComparisonOperator>Between</ogc:ComparisonOperator>
      </ogc:ComparisonOperators>
    </ogc:Scalar_Capabilities>
    <ogc:Id_Capabilities>
      <ogc:EID/>
      <ogc:FID/>
    </ogc:Id_Capabilities>
  </ogc:Filter_Capabilities>
</wfs:WFS_Capabilities>
